SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT * FROM (SELECT DISTINCT H.TNHD_ID, H.TNHD_PPR_ID, H.TNHD_MUTATIONCODE, P.PR_OMSCHRIJVING, HPP.HPP_HOLDERNUMMER, V.CONTRACT_ID, H.TNHD_ORIGIN, H.TNHD_USER FROM MF_TERMINATION_HDR H :1 INNER JOIN PRODUCTEN_PER_RELATIE PPR ON PPR.PPR_ID=H.TNHD_PPR_ID INNER JOIN HOLDERS_PER_PRODUCT HPP ON HPP.HPP_RELATIENUMMER=PPR.PPR_RELATIENUMMER AND HPP.HPP_PRODUCT=PPR.PPR_PRODUCTNUMMER AND HPP.HPP_PRODUCT_VOLGNR=PPR.PPR_VOLGNR_PER_PRODUCT AND HPP.HPP_TYPE_HOLDER=1 LEFT OUTER JOIN PRODUCTEN P ON P.PR_PRODUCTNUMMER=PPR.PPR_PRODUCTNUMMER INNER JOIN CLIENT_CONTRACT_VW V ON V.CLIENT_NR=PPR.PPR_RELATIENUMMER :4 :5 :6 :2 ORDER BY H.TNHD_ID DESC) :3
